		 Monkey Gems   BenBen the monkey needs your help! It looks like he got himself in some trouble with the local snakes by stealing their rattles. Help him fend off the colorful reptiles one by one in this fun and exciting match-making adventure! With three fantastic chapters, gorgeous visuals and engaging sound, Monkey Gems is one game you'll want to play over and over again!  
	 
		  
	 
	 
		
	 
	 
		
 
       
  
	 
 
	 
 
		 
		 
 
	 
		
			 
	 
