		 Crossword: Master   Are you ready to master a classic crossword challenge? Our online crossword puzzle game is an excellent way to spend some free time building your vocabulary and problem-solving skills, as well as a great way to keep your mind quick and flexible.  
	 
		  
	 
	 
		
	 
	 
		
 
       
  
	 
 
	 
 
		 
		 
 
	 
		
			 
	 
		 Mine-Finder   The goal of Mine-Finder is to find where all the mines are within a specific field of squares. To help you, the game shows a number in a square which tells you how many mines there are adjacent to that square. Can you work out where the mines are without detonating any of them?  
	 
		  
	 
	 
		
	 
	 
		
 
       
  
	 
 
	 
 
		 
	 
 
		 
	 
 
	 
 
		 
	 
 

 
	 
		  
	 
		 
